#

Sriracha Shrimp Burger

25 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

ShellfishEggs

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

SeafoodQuick MealSpicy

Description

A spicy and flavorful shrimp burger with a zesty kick from sriracha, perfect for a quick, satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 pound
  • panko breadcrumbs: 1/2 cup
  • mayonnaise: 1/4 cup
  • sriracha sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • green onion (finely chopped): 2
  • egg: 1
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • burger buns: 2
  • lettuce leaves: 2
  • sliced tomato: 1
